// Workspace file joining the modules that share Go code.
//
// Adding a module here lets every other listed module import it via
// its real module path (github.com/nexussacco/<name>) without a
// go.mod `replace` directive. Local filesystem paths are picked up
// automatically — handy for monorepo development and for the
// in-tree finance module that doesn't yet live in a registry.
//
// Dockerfiles must COPY the workspace + every listed module's
// source. See services/mpesa/Dockerfile and services/savings/Dockerfile
// for the multi-stage build pattern.

go 1.26.3

use (
	./services/finance
	./services/identity
	./services/member
	./services/mpesa
	./services/savings
)
